Why is losing titles and privileges of royalty seen as the queen being salty? Of course they should lose them if they do not want to perform their royal obligations. If they do not want to perform those duties, of course they should not get to keep the benefits.

The similar comparison with a republic would be if someone becomes president, but does not want to perform the presidential duties, and instead wants to spend their days watching TV, playing golf, and playing with their phone. Imagine how that would look!

Oh wait...
